cfg.h:
* Renamed MAX suffixes to CAP for consistency.
* Added: AOB_CAP. Defaults to size of a page on most systems.
* Renamed: LOG_STORE_CAP to LOG_AOB_CAP.

aob.c/.h:
* Basic AOB implementation. We will use these heavily. It is not an Arena
	allocator. Alignment will always be 1 or sizeof( x8 ). We will be slowly
	converting the Log, Src, and future modules like Intern to use them
	exclusively. This will help us cut down on tons of micro-allocations.
	The Log already does this with its .store, and Src should have it's own
	too.